#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.113"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.113:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.113:0.2"
msgid "11. Tikavagga"
msgstr "11. Triads"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.113:0.3"
msgid "113. Aratisutta"
msgstr "113. Dissatisfaction"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.448"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.113:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three things."

msgctxt "an6.113:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

#. VAR: vihiṃsā → vihesā (mr)
msgctxt "an6.113:1.3"
msgid "Arati, vihiṃsā, adhammacariyā."
msgstr "Dissatisfaction, cruelty, and unprincipled conduct."

msgctxt "an6.113:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā."
msgstr "These are the three things."

msgctxt "an6.113:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr "To give up these three things you should develop three things."

msgctxt "an6.113:1.6"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an6.113:1.7"
msgid ""
"Aratiyā pahānāya muditā bhāvetabbā, vihiṃsāya pahānāya avihiṃsā bhāvetabbā, "
"adhammacariyāya pahānāya dhammacariyā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr ""
"You should develop rejoicing to give up negativity, kindness to give up "
"cruelty, and principled conduct to give up unprincipled conduct."

msgctxt "an6.113:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya ime tayo dhammā "
"bhāvetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the three things you should develop to give up those three things.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.113:1.9"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
